    <h3>Co-Founder, CEO</h3>
    <div class="org">Speedscale Inc</div>
    <div class="dates">January 2020 – Present</div>
    <p>
      Speedscale automatically generates realistic API test suites for
      cloud-native architectures like Kubernetes. Launched August 2020, backed by
      Y Combinator, Sierra Ventures, Tech Square Ventures, Soma Capital, and
      others.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="exp">
    <h3>Co-Founder, CTO</h3>
    <div class="org">WiseCracker LLC</div>
    <div class="dates">July 2014 – Present</div>
    <p>
